author: abrinke1
body: Alex Madorsky loaded new firmware onto the EMTF boards at 2016-04-01, 11:37:13, with small changes to the SP output data format.  Also, I've added a permanent variable "mode", which is the 4-bit-station mode (the old "quality").  Alex has loaded a new 4-bit quality corresponding to the latest convention in the emulator.
title: Update to unpacker, new DAQ output format
